detaileddescription.para: Tests your typing speed and accuracy

sect1.title: Getting Started
sect1.para: Start the program, either login or sign up, You only need a username, and it will make a folder that saves every test you make

sect2.title: Installing
sect2.para: Just unpack the zip file, and open the Main.py file

sect1.title: Usage
sect1.para: After you have logged in, or signed in, you need to choose a difficulty, and from there you get a sentence you'll need to copy as fast as possible

sect1.title: Acknowledgments
sect1.para: I'll aknowlegde my current teacher Kenneth Hebel, and my former teacher Talha Mahmood Sheikh for teaching me how to make a program like this.
